cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DC, cs.AR 

This paper is about optimizing the performance of Convolutional Neural Network (CNN) model inference on CPUs. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). Other likely categories include cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing), and cs.AR (Hardware Architecture).
